This contains the windmc library that is used for
tasks for this capstone project.

The controller code (windmc.sim.MainTaskManager) is to be started from within
the controller directory.

The cluster code (windmc.sim.clusters.cluster) is to be started from
within the cluster directory.

Both the cluster and controller code should be started from within the
pythonlib no the windmc directory. start them with the -m option and 
use the package syntax:
python -m windmc.sim.tasks

